If I have a child,

00:26:53.160 --> 00:26:54.560
should it suffer with me?

00:26:55.550 --> 00:26:56.750
What do you want to do?

00:27:00.400 --> 00:27:01.160
Xiaojun.

00:27:04.720 --> 00:27:06.830
I really can't bear to do it.

00:27:09.790 --> 00:27:10.510
Could you go

00:27:11.070 --> 00:27:12.400
with her on behalf of me?

00:27:16.500 --> 00:27:19.030
[Sweet Barbershop]

00:27:19.030 --> 00:27:19.630
It's done.

00:27:23.110 --> 00:27:24.030
How much?

