Six yuan.

00:27:28.720 --> 00:27:29.680
Come often.

00:27:30.880 --> 00:27:31.440
Xiaojun.

00:27:32.720 --> 00:27:33.240
Ximei.

00:27:35.510 --> 00:27:37.110
It can't be delayed anymore.

00:27:38.920 --> 00:27:39.920
It's time.

00:27:41.200 --> 00:27:42.400
If we wait any longer,

00:27:43.510 --> 00:27:45.310
it won't be good for your health.

00:27:50.480 --> 00:27:52.080
Did Xiangdong tell you that?

00:27:55.750 --> 00:27:56.680
I'm sorry.

00:27:58.440 --> 00:27:59.500
It doesn't matter.

00:28:00.350 --> 00:28:01.480
It's not your fault.

00:28:04.240 --> 00:28:05.920
Fourth Brother, I'm going out for a while.

