What if

00:29:01.240 --> 00:29:02.400
something really goes wrong?

00:29:02.400 --> 00:29:03.480
I know.

00:29:03.880 --> 00:29:05.510
Don't worry. I'll hurry

00:29:05.590 --> 00:29:07.320
and get all the documents ready

00:29:07.350 --> 00:29:08.660
for legal operation.

00:29:09.000 --> 00:29:10.240
Then please do it quickly.

00:29:10.240 --> 00:29:11.030
We're leaving.

00:29:11.030 --> 00:29:11.360
Okay.

00:29:11.480 --> 00:29:12.000
Take care.

00:29:12.000 --> 00:29:12.530
Let's go.

00:29:13.350 --> 00:29:14.160
Take care.

00:29:14.400 --> 00:29:15.200
Do it quickly.

00:29:16.790 --> 00:29:17.640
You're here.

00:29:18.270 --> 00:29:19.310
Who needs to see the doctor?

00:29:19.310 --> 00:29:19.790
I do.

00:29:21.350 --> 00:29:22.350
Come in then.

00:29:25.750 --> 00:29:26.880
Wait for me a moment.

00:29:29.000 --> 00:29:30.600
Call me if you need anything.

00:29:31.550 --> 00:29:33.150
What seems to be the problem?

