making you and our child suffer with me.

00:34:54.840 --> 00:34:56.440
You've been through so much.

00:35:17.760 --> 00:35:18.690
I, Ni Xiangdong,

00:35:21.280 --> 00:35:23.680
will definitely make something of myself.

00:35:24.630 --> 00:35:25.360
Trust me.

00:35:26.710 --> 00:35:28.280
We'll have another child.

