I promise I'll give you

00:35:34.510 --> 00:35:35.510
a warm home.

00:36:05.230 --> 00:36:06.030
Our first child

00:36:06.030 --> 00:36:08.160
was probably less than 2 months along.

00:36:09.480 --> 00:36:10.670
The second child

00:36:13.400 --> 00:36:15.880
probably had hands, feet, and a heartbeat.

00:36:17.360 --> 00:36:19.290
When did you have the second child?

00:36:20.070 --> 00:36:21.000
2002.

00:36:21.320 --> 00:36:22.150
What happened

00:36:22.920 --> 00:36:23.520
back then?

00:36:25.440 --> 00:36:26.970
It was an accident, I guess.

00:36:27.110 --> 00:36:28.770
Ni Xiangdong got into trouble

00:36:29.000 --> 00:36:30.630
with some gangsters outside.

00:36:30.630 --> 00:36:32.110
They came to our home.

00:36:34.150 --> 00:36:35.410
And then I miscarried.

00:36:37.840 --> 00:36:39.110
Do you believe

00:36:39.960 --> 00:36:41.380
that what goes around comes around?

00:36:41.380 --> 00:36:42.920
[No Smoking]

00:36:42.920 --> 00:36:44.030
I certainly don't.

00:36:45.480 --> 00:36:47.740
Are children blessings or karmic debts?

00:36:50.070 --> 00:36:50.880
Back then,

00:36:51.150 --> 00:36:51.370
Guo Adi got in trouble for smuggling.

00:36:51.370 --> 00:36:53.230
[No Smoking]

00:36:53.230 --> 00:36:54.290
You ran to the city.

00:36:56.110 --> 00:36:56.800
After all you've been through,

00:36:56.800 --> 00:36:58.300
why would you still be with someone

00:36:58.300 --> 00:36:59.360
like Ni Xiangdong?

00:37:01.030 --> 00:37:02.440
What kind of person do you think he is?

00:37:02.440 --> 00:37:03.100
A deadbeat.

00:37:03.710 --> 00:37:04.710
To put it bluntly,

00:37:04.960 --> 00:37:05.880
a hooligan.

00:37:07.030 --> 00:37:08.480
You probably don't understand

00:37:08.480 --> 00:37:09.670
that people like us

00:37:09.760 --> 00:37:11.490
who haven't had much education

00:37:11.510 --> 00:37:12.230
don't have many paths

00:37:12.230 --> 00:37:13.110
to take.

00:37:13.960 --> 00:37:14.930
Everyone's life

00:37:14.960 --> 00:37:15.590
is like glutinous rice balls

00:37:15.590 --> 00:37:17.050
made by children's hands.

00:37:18.070 --> 00:37:19.870
Some are big, and some are small.

00:37:20.440 --> 00:37:22.070
There's no logic to it.

00:37:23.070 --> 00:37:24.670
Just whatever mood strikes.

00:37:27.110 --> 00:37:28.000
Maybe when making them,

00:37:28.000 --> 00:37:29.930
they didn't even wash their hands.

00:37:30.280 --> 00:37:32.360
And the dirt got kneaded in too.

00:37:35.920 --> 00:37:37.650
There's no pure white or black;

00:37:38.400 --> 00:37:39.960
it's just a gray rice ball.

00:37:42.590 --> 00:37:43.670
Who can withstand

00:37:44.800 --> 00:37:47.260
being torn apart
and scrutinized like that?

00:37:48.510 --> 00:37:51.280
How can anyone guarantee
they're completely clean?

00:37:51.280 --> 00:37:52.510
No one ever taught us,

00:37:53.230 --> 00:37:54.030
and we can't tell

00:37:54.030 --> 00:37:55.290
what's right or wrong.

00:37:55.920 --> 00:37:57.450
No matter what path we take,

00:37:57.710 --> 00:37:59.310
it's just about making money

00:37:59.440 --> 00:38:00.300
and getting by.

00:38:01.110 --> 00:38:02.440
We just want to survive.

00:38:04.030 --> 00:38:05.710
If things were so good with Ni Xiangdong,

00:38:05.710 --> 00:38:06.280
why did you

00:38:06.280 --> 00:38:07.630
end up with Cao Xiaojun

00:38:08.590 --> 00:38:09.650
and even marry him?

00:38:12.190 --> 00:38:13.550
Even the sweetest candy

00:38:15.920 --> 00:38:17.520
will eventually turn bitter

00:38:18.030 --> 00:38:18.890
if overcooked.

00:38:40.550 --> 00:38:42.010
Close that door properly.

00:38:42.480 --> 00:38:44.680
The light is making it hard to see the TV.

00:39:18.550 --> 00:39:19.320
I'm going out for a while.

00:39:19.320 --> 00:39:20.070
Don't wait up for me tonight.

00:39:20.070 --> 00:39:21.270
I might not come back.

00:39:21.510 --> 00:39:22.280
Where are you going?

00:39:22.280 --> 00:39:23.320
Dinner is ready.

00:39:24.280 --> 00:39:25.080
I'm going out.

00:39:25.110 --> 00:39:26.280
A friend needs to see me.

00:39:26.280 --> 00:39:28.280
You're going to see
the person surnamed Liang again?

00:39:28.280 --> 00:39:29.840
When did I say that?

00:39:30.190 --> 00:39:31.760
A friend of mine needs to see me.

00:39:31.760 --> 00:39:33.760
You've gambled away your motorbike.

00:39:33.760 --> 00:39:34.900
They lent you money to gamble.

00:39:34.900 --> 00:39:36.150
It's obviously a trap.

00:39:36.150 --> 00:39:36.920
Are you stupid?

00:39:36.920 --> 00:39:38.230
And you're walking right into it!

00:39:38.230 --> 00:39:39.480
When did I gamble?

00:39:40.070 --> 00:39:41.320
I'm going out to make money!

00:39:41.320 --> 00:39:42.710
Who's going to support you
if I don't make money?

00:39:42.710 --> 00:39:43.800
You're not going!

00:39:44.360 --> 00:39:45.280
Stupid!

00:39:45.840 --> 00:39:47.250
Don't go!

00:39:47.280 --> 00:39:49.000
Can you just stay put for one day?

00:39:49.000 --> 00:39:50.400
What are you trying to do?

00:39:50.920 --> 00:39:51.880
I need to go out for a bit!

00:39:51.880 --> 00:39:52.710
Yet you won't let me!

00:39:52.710 --> 00:39:53.240
My period

00:39:53.760 --> 00:39:54.590
is late.

00:39:55.230 --> 00:39:56.000
What's late?

00:39:58.230 --> 00:40:00.630
I thought I couldn't get pregnant anymore.

00:40:07.150 --> 00:40:08.880
Uncle Chen has been arrested.

00:40:09.150 --> 00:40:10.230
One after another.

00:40:11.030 --> 00:40:12.030
It never ends.

00:40:12.440 --> 00:40:14.640
How will we raise our child if it's born?

00:40:15.000 --> 00:40:16.330
It's not the right time.

00:40:17.840 --> 00:40:19.280
Well, tomorrow morning,

00:40:19.360 --> 00:40:20.800
I'll come and take you

00:40:20.880 --> 00:40:21.880
to the clinic

00:40:22.030 --> 00:40:23.090
to get an abortion.

00:41:28.070 --> 00:41:29.920
Ximei, are you okay?

00:42:39.480 --> 00:42:40.760
You shouldn't smoke.

00:42:49.000 --> 00:42:50.730
I'm having an abortion anyway.

00:42:51.710 --> 00:42:52.770
It doesn't matter.

00:43:09.800 --> 00:43:11.230
Uncle Chen once said

00:43:13.880 --> 00:43:15.280
I had been through too much,

00:43:15.280 --> 00:43:17.080
and my body had long been ruined.

00:43:21.480 --> 00:43:22.110
This might be

00:43:22.110 --> 00:43:23.360
my last child.

00:43:37.280 --> 00:43:38.960
If you really want this baby,

00:43:42.320 --> 00:43:43.190
keep it.

00:43:46.880 --> 00:43:47.630
He said...

00:43:48.550 --> 00:43:49.480
Never mind him.

00:43:52.840 --> 00:43:54.400
It's your body.

00:43:56.510 --> 00:43:57.640
It's your decision.

00:43:58.630 --> 00:43:59.920
I'm just a woman,

00:44:01.440 --> 00:44:02.770
with little education.

00:44:03.070 --> 00:44:04.400
I can't earn much money.

00:44:05.000 --> 00:44:06.260
How can I raise a child?

00:44:18.800 --> 00:44:19.860
If the baby is born,

00:44:21.510 --> 00:44:21.920
I'll raise it.